sg":"情緒上腦個陣好難理智咁去解決問題喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我覺得意識到有問題個陣已經係改變既第一步"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:43:08.000Z","msg":"我承認可能自己開post果陣太隨意就話想自殺<br />\n不過好多時候人自殺真係一念之差<br />\n<br />\n但我有啲心結解唔開都係事實<br />\nAnyway多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8127c509aaf80a4f8edf7628316f59edb97dfb7","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"07c2f482748447666e961655d372d62b97cae12b","tid":2192110,"uid":352661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95c97d263ef6b17025fd3f5dfc1a3d251bfd3cf4","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27ae0f18e9130b09fe1adb5717d6671b1f3d78a6","tid":2192110,"uid":352661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:43:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:07:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:45:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db9505aa3bd6882335ff7ce0b6d1c87708ae6e4","tid":2192110,"uid":16981,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"193752e8e2168c957ea939971c9b1e60fb9f3582","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b6194e02bf649c6c3099d750a94cef4e193d93","tid":2192110,"uid":16981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfd6a4a23c666111978f8e9187b4fad96f332f8","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"我會唔會係下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:11:08.000Z","msg":"認真答:<br />\n唔會係下一個, 因為喺你考慮期間已經有好多人因為咁而自殺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T03:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"若要生活好..."},{"pid":"b608924e3a97e0b266f63deb4f9ec7d87ea2d8e0","tid":2192110,"uid":312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:04:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1125b8a5ea683848ad9f515fe8bb8a6b8aabee3a","tid":2192110,"uid":125898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T06:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e04e55d730eca24683f9c456102ebb7af84cc4a0","tid":2192110,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1bfd6a4a23c666111978f8e9187b4fad96f332f8","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T02:19:01.000Z","msg":"我會唔會係下一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T11:04:32.000Z","msg":"相信你心中一定非常痛苦，才會如此寫下你的心聲！雖然，我並未完全了解你，但我明白置身痛苦中是怎樣一回事。有些人在困苦之中，會選擇放棄自己，不知道你是否也有這自殺的念頭？<br />\n <br />\n無論你是否想過放棄自己，我也希望你不要將困擾藏在心裡。因為人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。你不如停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=YmBpLFXYotmGfWLbQLkNp%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=8ab756af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事、有趣短片，也有與自殺有關的人與事，你可以隨心看看。您更可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n <br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"9d206914ff305348c4fa8dfcf46964011a32bc51","tid":2192110,"uid":122826,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T14:15:07.000Z","msg":"唔好睇咁多心靈雞湯<br />\n只會愈陷愈深<br />\n人可以做既得兩樣<br />\n唔滿意現狀就放棄安逸 一係贏盡一係仆街<br />\n唔係就接受現實做行屍走肉等死"},{"pid":"5305a42580a6ac66b19a89274557b6fa8d2809fe","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:52:31.000Z","msg":"訓唔著，唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a08525a43ffc03236397ed4e6f6133ec44b95a","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T20:59:35.000Z","msg":"見到你同男朋友既合照，我知道你已經忘記左我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9e5cd8e75b665c10cc0c9fa2bec86a03dbac3d","tid":2192110,"uid":105425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99f9dc7eef8ccd5b35060dadba507a9c95d1c3be","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9e5cd8e75b665c10cc0c9fa2bec86a03dbac3d","tid":2192110,"uid":105425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:07:51.000Z","msg":"你咁識為人設想，會唔會代表你對世界仲有留戀"},{"pid":"21002446f3b90ccc944090840d7bb9a812734a59","tid":2192110,"uid":105425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99f9dc7eef8ccd5b35060dadba507a9c95d1c3be","tid":2192110,"uid":78243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a9e5cd8e75b665c10cc0c9fa2bec86a03dbac3d","tid":2192110,"uid":105425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:02:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:07:51.000Z","msg":"你咁識為人設想，會唔會代表你對世界仲有留戀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bdf62eb730e1ddb30f01421a72bd5f6f0ab740a","tid":2192110,"uid":229459,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T22:29:10.000Z","msg":"You are not alone<br />\n唔好理屋企人對你喱個「大學生」有咩期望<br />\n<br />\n全香港大部份大學生對比起廿年前人工都無乜點變過，要有「前」途同「錢」途只能夠做政府工，喺香港淨係得政府工追到正常通脹